---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Courses">
  <h1>Courses</h1>

  <h2>Current Courses</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Programming for Lawyers</strong>: From 2024 this course was redesigned to emphasize
      teaching aspects of programming through the task of creating data visualizations. Co-taught
      with Lucas Thevenard Gomes.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Legal Data Science</strong>: Course teaches data wrangling, how to think about
      quantitative problems within the legal field, how to answer them through the python data
      framework and how to create and read basic statistical models and tests. Materials available at
      <a href="https://github.com/joseluizn/cdj-fgvdireitorio">Github page</a>.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Past Courses</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Programming for Lawyers</strong>: Course format until 2023. Focused directly on Python
      programming languages aspects and structures.
      <a href="https://github.com/joseluizn/progr-adv-fgvdireitorio">Materials available at Github</a>.
    </li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
